,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T12:48:47.000Z","msg":"做完運動再推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feb18c45ec5418f3ffa81bc2fd0c4cff2ed1db73","tid":1850260,"uid":47966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T12:48:48.000Z","msg":"Building Service WS/AI/Inspector受唔受"},{"pid":"8754405d59052fbfa88ce13fe1c2f4a76e4b4ddd","tid":1850260,"uid":177243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"feb18c45ec5418f3ffa81bc2fd0c4cff2ed1db73","tid":1850260,"uid":47966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T12:48:48.000Z","msg":"Building Service WS/AI/Inspector受唔受"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T12:50:16.000Z","msg":"受，在職工程相關就得"},{"pid":"2c3bc858bd8c1e6a929b2e4d7163960de7b972ef","tid":1850260,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T12:50:21.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af6e95acfdb93ceb65846b16ea6feb360c95c8ea","tid":1850260,"uid":24140,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T13:04:57.000Z","msg":"想想問問年費成400蚊一年好似貴左少少？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f74d2a35c15cb2e8e5d38d524a695acd9933f217","tid":1850260,"uid":10503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T13:08:00.000Z","msg":"聽日見<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a5b28d3d1ef45f709b5035ac9612a91d3b68e27","tid":1850260,"uid":11602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T13:08:41.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2a9ca5c524a41fca668382ccd1111184b5b611f5","tid":1850260,"uid":289946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T13:09:00.000Z","msg":"800舊好貴，入完有咩用? 立法會投到工程界別?"},{"pid":"1be1dcbeb0c68e36067721956e52ab6dcdeb015f","tid":1850260,"uid":48334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T13:09:52.000Z","msg":"$800<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dd5c35652d0a97bf1765edcff47800dfb12c795","tid":1850260,"uid":270082,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"af6e95acfdb93ceb65846b16ea6feb360c95c8ea","tid":1850260,"uid":24140,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T13:04:57.000Z","msg":"想想問問年費成400蚊一年好似貴左少少？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T13:11:21.000Z","msg":"正式會員一年係800先啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n**copy from tg channel**<br />\nQ:點解你地工會年費收成800蚊一年咁貴﹐你地係咪食人血饅頭<br />\nA: 因為新成立既工會﹐好多硬件設備野都要設置﹐而且根據之前既問卷調查﹐比較多人希望成為獨立工會。但係我地籌委會成員全部都係素人﹐冇任何金主/大額捐贈﹐所以好需要大家既年費做資金﹐若果之後資金充裕﹐理事會係可以減免某一年既會員費。<br />\n另外﹐工會都需要一筆款項去支援一啲因為工業/政治問題而有需要既會員﹐而且未來若果有任何工業行動﹐所需既款項其實都唔細﹐最後我地亦參考咗其他國家工會﹐<br />\n如韓國工會為10USD/month﹐澳洲工會10AUD/week為指標﹐最後選擇咗依個數目。"},{"pid":"dfa3e49fe1cc09705fcb1e00ffa5030aaaf14d91","tid":1850260,"uid":65790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T13:15:13.000Z","msg":"我就係覺得呢個工會太雜所以未入<br />\n可唔可以搞d細既分會<br />\n<br />\n利申:HKIA"},{"pid":"48529509dd0456790ebcbb5f2c07eddfcc76d43d","tid":1850260,"uid":108512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T13:15:18.000Z","msg":"800 真係貴左d<br />\n180 都叫可接受<br />\n工程雜工800 蚊係一日人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15ec63c0264dcdc6c0d32ddaa9aed14901630de9","tid":1850260,"uid":196227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dfa3e49fe1cc09705fcb1e00ffa5030aaaf14d91","tid":1850260,"uid":65790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T13:15:13.000Z","msg":"我就係覺得呢個工會太雜所以未入<br />\n可唔可以搞d細既分會<br />\n<br />\n利申:HKIA"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T13:20:43.000Z","msg":"咁多獨立工會你想做撚死人咩<br />\n行政費都貴到仆街<br />\n<br />\n工程本身藍到仆街，你唔集合可能一個工會都做唔到"},{"pid":"de52c1ec7de82c912881dd6fc7ef0970139fb936","tid":1850260,"uid":65790,"like":0,"dislike